'''Kutloanong Location''' is a township located between [[Welkom]] and [[Allanridge]] in the [[Free State (province)|Free State]], South Africa.
It falls under the Municipality of Lejweleputsa and it is a township to an old town [[Odendaalsrus]].
It is well known for producing soccer stars such as [[Kamohelo Mokotjo]], Khotso Moleko, [[Vuyisile Wana]] etc.{{Citation needed|date=January 2015}}

